Taiwo Owatemi (amụrụ na 22 Julaị 1992) bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị Britain bụ onye omeiwu (MP) maka Coventry North West kemgbe 2019. Onye otu Labour Party, ọ bụ Minista Nchịkọta maka Ụmụ nwanyị na Ịha nhata site na Septemba 2021 ruo Septemba 2022.
Owatemi tolitere na Plumstead, na njikọ chiri anya na ezinụlọ ya site na nwanne nne ya na ụmụ nwanne nne ya nọ na Coventry
Nna ya nwụrụ mgbe ọ dị afọ isii
Ọ bụ nne ya, onye nọọsụ, zụlitere ya na ejima ya na nwanne ya nwoke nke okenye.

Owatemi nwere nzere masta na Mahadum Kent ma ruo eruo dị ka onye na-ahụ maka ọgwụ. Ọ rụrụ ọrụ dị ka onye na-ahụ maka ọgwụ na ngalaba ọrịa kansa na Dartford na Gravesham NHS Trust tupu ọ banye na Nzukọ Ndị Omeiwu.

A họpụtara Owatemi maka ọrụ nkuzi nke ndị omeiwu site na Social Mobility Foundation ma nweta ahụmịhe na-arụ ọrụ n'ọfịs Westminster nke onye omeiwu Conservative Oliver Letwin. Ọ rụrụ ọrụ n'ọtụtụ ọrụ na Young Fabians ma bipụta akwụkwọ gbasara iwu ahụike. Ọ bụ gọvanọ nke ụlọ akwụkwọ praịmarị dị n'ógbè ahụ site na 2016.
A họpụtara ya dị ka onye na-azọ ọkwa onye ọrụ maka Coventry North West na ntuli aka 2019 mgbe onye omeiwu Labour nọ n'ọkwa, Geoffrey Robinson, kwupụtara ebumnuche ya ịkwụsị
Owatemi nwere oche maka Labour na ọnụ ọgụgụ ka ukwuu nke vootu 208. Ọ bụ otu n'ime ụmụ nwanyị atọ a họpụtara site na Coventry na 2019, ndị ọzọ bụ Zarah Sultana na Colleen Fletcher.
Na ntuli aka ndị isi Labour Party nke afọ 2020, Owatemi họpụtara Lisa Nandy.

Owatemi jere ozi dị ka odeakwụkwọ onwe onye nke ndị omeiwu (PPS) nye odeakwụkwọ ụlọ onyinyo, Nick Thomas-Symonds, site na Eprel 2020 ruo Septemba 2021. A họpụtara ya dị ka Minista Nchịkọta maka Ụmụ nwanyị na Ịha nhata na Septemba 2021. Ọ gbara arụkwaghịm n'ọkwa a na 7 Septemba 2022.
